---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Read Kitchen Explored's privacy policy to understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit our site.">

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <nav class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-navy transition-colors">Home</a>
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/></svg>
      <span class="text-gray-600">Privacy Policy</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none prose-headings:text-navy prose-a:text-orange-start">
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Last updated: January 2025</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        Kitchen Explored does not collect personal information beyond standard server logs. When you
        visit our site, your browser may send standard request headers (IP address, browser type,
        referring page) which are stored temporarily in server logs.
      </p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We may use analytics tools such as Google Analytics to understand how visitors use the site.
        These tools may set cookies and collect anonymised usage data. You can opt out via your browser
        settings or a browser extension.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        Some product links on this site are affiliate links. If you click a link and make a purchase,
        we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. This helps support the site.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy? Email us at{' '}
        <a href="mailto:hello@kitchenexplored.com">hello@kitchenexplored.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
